Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,RETURN OF THE GREAT HERO
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In your last moments, you were one of us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You were...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}our friend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Up you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you've matured well, Popp.\NIt's been quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not... You can't be Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The real Master wouldn't\Nsuddenly return after all this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a dream or an illusion\Nor that dirty Zaboera in disguise again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.81,0:02:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not possible, Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a Magic Circle of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a perfectly disguised\Ndark sorcerer couldn't cast it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Leona, is that...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is... Is it really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me for\Ncausing you all such concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am neither ghost\Nnor imposter nor illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And obviously not an identical stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really the real me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Howl, Inferno!{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! {\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Northern Grand Blade!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Queen Flora?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I sensed something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.96,0:04:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-Master!\N-Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my! My good clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it!\NI just wanna hug you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Down you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, I sensed your Magic Power\Nfrom a long distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Your power was most impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown a lot, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those clothes... I never expected you\Nto become a Martial Artist, Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.71,0:05:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have truly become an impressive Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You all have changed so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without me,\Nthrough your own strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to see you all come so far\Nmakes me sincerely proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you've devoted yourself\Nto a never-ending battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're allowed to express\Nyour honest emotions sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,These are... my honest emotions, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I suppose this is what it means...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to be unable to show one's face.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bartos was the strongest knight\Nof the Dark Army...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The malice you sense in my blade is\Nmy hatred towards you, my father's killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not all students of Aban\Nrespect their teacher and love justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them love violence\Nand have embraced the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,After seeing just how weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,justice really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.68,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the Six Legion Commanders\Nof the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, the Undead Legion Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't deserve your forgiveness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I bet this is our chance\Nto see Hyunckel be all weepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rare sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, don't be like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can anyone blame me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him be for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, Hyunckel was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.51,0:07:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright. You don't need to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're here now,\Ngiving your strength to help the others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That alone brings me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It brings me great joy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Leona. You're here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I was given this by Queen Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. If she deemed you worthy,\Nthen I trust her judgement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Aban, please explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you come back after dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told you died on Dermline Island\Nduring your battle with Hadorra.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back then, Master...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A spell?! Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be out of Magic Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This spell requires\Nvery little Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, it turns life energy\Ninto explosive power to defeat enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.34,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! This spell is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, Dai! I leave the rest to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&H00FF00&}Megante!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Master tried to protect us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...and cast Megante.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If anyone other than a Priest\Ncasts Megante,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,their body is obliterated\Nand they can't be resurrected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mean to doubt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but please tell us what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I never really died!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.59,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}DORAGORAMU{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NFIRE DRAGON TRANSFORMATION SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:20.59,On Top,,0,0,0,,REAPER FLUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been alive this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But, back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But we saw you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told you died!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that even possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like yourself, I too was given\Nsomething by Queen Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This... is what saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Amulet of Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Amulet of Carl\Nthat's passed down in the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it will help you someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Back when I went to face Dark Lord Hadorra,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Queen Flora gave me this treasure\Nof her royal family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&H00FF00&}Megante!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the explosion from my Megante spell,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this was damaged in my stead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's basically a kind of protection item.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, I managed to survive,\Nthough only barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you show up\Nto help before now, Master?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We risked our lives to fight\Nbecause we believed you had died!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.34,0:12:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying\Nyou knew this whole time and did nothing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Do you know how much\NI grieved when I heard you'd died?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We all fought desperately for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be some reason, right Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, I will explain in due time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you all to run\Nto the central palace as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to race\Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just answer the question and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All I have to say right now is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.61,0:13:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me when I tell you that I am here\Nto defeat the Dark King like all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I am no longer your Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a new ally who will fight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I haven't regained the stamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you, everyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. You seem alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately for you, I'm quite immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Immortal! Immortal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Piercing my heart\Nisn't nearly enough to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I was interrupted earlier\Nby Hadorra in his dying moments
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but I won't be stopped again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,My instincts tell me that\NI can't afford to let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead... if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did Master suddenly\Ntell us to run to the palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.55,0:15:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How should we know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But if Master says to run,\Nwe obey and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It may seem meaningless or unimportant,\Nbut there's always a reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's always been Master Aban's style.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead if I can, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.07,0:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew I was alive,\Nyet you sent the others off regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be quite confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That sort of attitude will cost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You impressed me by thwarting\Nmy Nine of Diamonds,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but that wasn't my only Kill Trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The others won't be able to\Nproceed unharmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter what powerful spells you have,\NI doubt you can do anything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Reaper... or whatever they call you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,do those Kill Traps of yours activate\Nautomatically when someone snares them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Those sorts of traps tend to be activated\Nby the creator's Magic Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But your hands appear full at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this your plan all along?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.84,0:16:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,By keeping me here, all the Kill Traps\Nto King Ban's palace won't activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you sent them ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're quite sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're more dangerous than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough chit chat. It's time to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:17:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I'll wipe out the others\Nwith new Kill Traps.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of my Kill Traps\Nare in the palace anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That's useful information.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep that in mind down the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.22,0:17:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need a shave, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I already had one before I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My arm, no, half my body won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Where did this feather come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.87,0:17:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When you first fell,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I still sensed malice,\Nso I took precautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it feel to be caught\Nin a magical trap yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:18:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra was once a cruel man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He did terrible things to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But he always did it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When fighting me,\Nhe always came forward to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But you are far lower than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You sit back and enjoy watching\Nthe people you trap suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lower than cruel, you're barbaric!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A warrior takes pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in upholding the basic rules of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,At least Hadorra understood that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,With this blow, feel the anger\Nof his departed soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.82,0:19:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I don't enjoy using it,\NI'm also well versed in such spellcraft.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you continue using such dirty traps\Nagainst us, I will fight back in kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you would be wise to remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear... I swear I will kill you\Nwith my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:20:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.59,0:20:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So King Ban is in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Whoa. It's even\Nmore impressive up close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.24,0:20:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. It's quite big, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Master?! Where did you come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.00,0:20:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We ran here at top speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was just a step\Nbehind you the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's lying.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I never sensed him behind us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know he remained back there for a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:21:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I used my new skill,\NSneaky Step Stealthy Step Aban Step.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not Sneaky Step\NStealthy Step Popp Step?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess if you used it,\Nyou could call it that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something about him\Nis different from before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like he possesses\Na completely different power.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That glow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it! So that's it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This man...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, everyone, for your next task...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.11,0:21:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see the extent of your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel... the extent of my power?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Far too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To be honest I was clumsy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:12.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}omoeba boku wa bukiyou de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it took me forever to get here{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.35,0:22:18.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shouganaikurai tomawarishita{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used even loneliness as a weapon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:23.98,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kodokukannsura mo buki ni shite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I searched the dungeon for a simple answer{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:29.91,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tannjun na kotae wo sagashita dannjon{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I cast aside\NRightness and kindness{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:35.75,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tadashisa yasashisa nagedashite mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just want to be there for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:41.88,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tada hitori kimi no mikata de itai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.04,0:22:47.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu koto ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is harder than any magic spell{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:53.51,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ari to arayuru mahou yori muzukashikute{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even though you're so close to me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:59.31,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}konnani mo chikaku ni itanoni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:01.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aishiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:05.23,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}imasara kizuitanosa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:10.36,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kimi no namae wo yobu tame ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Must be the reason I was born{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:16.79,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}boku wa kitto umarete kitannda{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shake off the clinging night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:22.71,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}shigamitsuku yoru furihodoite{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And go to see you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.88,0:23:25.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ai ni iku{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now to where you are{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:30.18,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ima sugu kimi no moto e{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel voices his objection to Aban.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The others continue hesitantly\Nbut their way is barred by a giant gate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its door is like the one\NDai and Baran barely managed to breach.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet Aban tackles it alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The mystery behind Aban's activities\Nafter his fight with Hadorra are revealed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:23:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.49,0:23:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Secret Way of Purification"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.00,0:24:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
